  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a Reaction, when you see a creature within 60 feet of you cast a Ninjutsu, Taijutsu, or Bukijutsu that would deal damage, you can cast a Bukijutsu you know with a casting time of 1 Action. </p><p>This Bukijutsu gains the Clash keyword if it didn't prior, and you immediately initiate a Clash. </p><p>If the triggering Ninjutsu does not have the Clash keyword, they make their Clash check at disadvantage. </p><p>You may use this feature twice per short rest.</p>",
